b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. LOVO AI is best suited for voiceover for videos, multi language content, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Murf AI, meanwhile, shines for corporate presentations, e learning voiceovers, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, LOVO AI describes itself as \"AI voiceover and text-to-speech platform.\" Murf AI, established in 2020, positions itself as \"Professional AI voiceovers for enterprise content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Murf AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean LOVO AI is a poor choice — far from it. LOVO AI excels in its own right, particularly for voiceover for videos and multi language content.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value professional voice quality, go with Murf AI. If 500+ voices in 100 languages matters more to you, LOVO AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
